---
title: Tangy Double-Stacked Beef Burgers with German-Style Potato Salad
description: Pan-fried, crispy, beefy goodness! This burger has all the toppings to take your meal to the next level: crunchy pickles and savoury caramelized onions – we've even chopped up some pickles to add zing to our classic potato salad. It's safe to say you won't miss out on BBQ with this stovetop-friendly dinner!
